# Game of Thrones Quiz

Welcome to the Game of Thrones Quiz! Test your knowledge of the epic fantasy series with this interactive quiz application.


## Introduction
This quiz application is built to challenge your knowledge of the Game of Thrones series. It covers a variety of questions related to the characters, events, and lore of the Seven Kingdoms.

## Features
- Interactive quiz with multiple-choice questions.
- Progress bar to track your advancement through the quiz.
- Display of correct answers and user's performance at the end of the quiz.
- Ability to restart the quiz and try again.
- User-friendly interface with a modal for adding new questions.

## Usage
1. Enter your username in the provided field before starting the quiz or adding a new question.
2. Open the quiz by clicking the "Start Quiz" button.
3. Answer each question by selecting the correct option.
4. Click "Next" to proceed to the next question.
5. At the end of the quiz, view your score and the correct answers.
6. Optionally, click "Show Answers" to review your responses.
7. Restart the quiz to challenge yourself again.

### Adding New Questions
1. Enter your username in the provided field.
2. Click on "Add Question" to open the modal.
3. Provide a new question and options.
4. Mark the correct option.
5. Click "Submit" to add the question to the quiz.

Note: Please ensure all fields, including the username, are filled before starting the quiz or adding a new question.

